I was like, "OK, here we go."

40:22.220 --> 40:23.955
[laughs]

40:25.356 --> 40:29.327
My first job was putting them
on the MTV tour.

40:29.427 --> 40:31.963
- It was gonna be
our first tour in America--

40:32.063 --> 40:35.567
a 107 city tour
in eight months--

40:35.667 --> 40:37.769
