47:12.931 --> 47:15.233
a long time and had seen a lot.

47:15.333 --> 47:17.235
- Man, I think Milli Vanilli
doing crack.

47:17.335 --> 47:18.636
I don't think--
[laughter]

47:18.736 --> 47:20.505
- It seemed bad to
a lot of these folks.

47:20.605 --> 47:22.974
- Those pants too tight.
They going--

47:23.074 --> 47:24.809
- They knew something was up.

47:24.910 --> 47:27.345
[cheers and applause]

47:27.445 --> 47:29.414
- Privately, I thought, like,

47:29.514 --> 47:32.383
you know, "Did they really
sing everything?"

47:32.483 --> 47:34.285
- Girls!
crowd: Girls!

47:34.385 --> 47:36.988
- Hey, boys!
crowd: Hey, boys!

47:37.088 --> 47:39.958
- Yeah!
crowd: Yeah!

47:40.058 --> 47:43.628
- * Girl, you know it's--
