They were gonna catch us
at some point or another.

48:30.075 --> 48:31.676
*

48:36.681 --> 48:40.018
*

48:40.118 --> 48:43.521
This load on our shoulders,

48:43.621 --> 48:46.657
it was getting heavy and heavy
