in a TV show,

52:26.944 --> 52:28.179
it's my voice.

52:28.279 --> 52:32.217
Music is from Frank Farian
and not from Milli Vanilli.

52:32.317 --> 52:39.257
*

52:40.325 --> 52:43.060
And Frank denied it all.

52:43.160 --> 52:46.297
His words were--I can
remember them to the day--

52:46.397 --> 52:49.267
"This artist is a liar.

52:49.367 --> 52:52.036
"Look the way he's dressed.

52:52.136 --> 52:53.971
"The Black guy.

52:54.071 --> 52:55.506
He's just trying to
make money."

52:55.606 --> 52:58.008
*

53:08.953 --> 53:10.054
- Ingrid!

53:10.154 --> 53:11.789
She said,
"Frank don't want you to be

53:11.889 --> 53:15.025
"talking out there to nobody.
